re>\n                    <figure>\n                        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg45wGDSlqAT1omWjvPioPZ0iO8hjJzbPfnRnKEquVz4a_xuokHUsKcZzmA-XMUkI33zlSRrazy65YmqZAXjjlc1pa2a29KE_onrmpvCYKi6Yl5mSFZ81qj5cG1iZzY1JGDM0ZHo9EpvSNY/s16000/xnautilusdesktop003.jpg\" alt=\"Atur rotasi video menjadi 90, 180, atau 270 derajat\">\n                        <figcaption>4. Centang opsi <strong>Transform</strong> dan pilih rotasi yang sesuai (misalnya, <strong>Rotate by 180 degrees</strong>).</figcaption>\n                    </figure>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n            <section class=\"social-sharing\">\n                <div id=\"pesbukdiskus\"></div>\n            </section>"
